# NBS-LMS Project Structure Guide

## Core Files
- Main entry: [src/main.js](mdc:src/main.js) - initializes the Vue application
- App component: [src/App.vue](mdc:src/App.vue) - root Vue component
- Vite config: [vite.config.mjs](mdc:vite.config.mjs) - build and dev server configuration
- Package.json: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - project dependencies and scripts

## Key Directories
- Components: [src/components/](mdc:src/components) - Reusable Vue components
- Views: [src/views/](mdc:src/views) - Page components
- Router: [src/router/](mdc:src/router) - Vue Router configuration
- Stores: [src/stores/](mdc:src/stores) - Pinia 狀態儲存 & 表單狀態控制 (含錯誤)
- Services: [src/services/](mdc:src/services) - 負責 API 通訊與資料格式轉換
- Composables: [src/composables/](mdc:src/composables) - 表單邏輯，如 useFormValidation
- Schemas: [src/schemas/](mdc:src/schemas) - 表單欄位 schema, mapping 規則
- Utils: [src/utils/](mdc:src/utils) - deep clone, deep compare 等共用方法
- Mocks: [src/mocks/](mdc:src/mocks) - MSW API mocking

## Configuration
- Styles: [src/style.css](mdc:src/style.css) - Global CSS
- UnoCSS: [uno.config.js](mdc:uno.config.js) - UnoCSS configuration
- Vercel: [vercel.json](mdc:vercel.json) - Vercel deployment configuration

## Appwrite Integration
- Appwrite client: [src/appwrite.js](mdc:src/appwrite.js) - Appwrite SDK setup
